headline: ‘Blue Sky’ Takes Flight: JetBlue and United Loyalty Members Can Now Earn and Redeem Across Both Airlines
summary: NEW YORK & CHICAGO, October 23, 2025--JetBlue (Nasdaq: JBLU) and United Airlines (Nasdaq: UAL) today launched the first major customer benefit from their Blue Sky collaboration: loyalty members of both airlines can now earn and redeem points or miles across each other’s networks.
